turns.ai_line: Good morning Doctor. I dey feel pains for my belle after I chop leftover rice wey I keep for house. I don also dey purge and I dey feel like to vomit. My place na very moist area and food dey spoil quick for here. I need your help to know wetin dey cause this wahala.

"Doctor, e get any test wey you fit do to check wetin dey worry me? I no understand why na just after I chop the rice na im dis tin start. I hope say no be something serious. I never see dis kind thing happen before o."

"Abeg doctor, I dey wait for any advice wey you fit give me. I pray say no be something wey go stop me from chop rice because na my favorite food be that o. Since dat time wey I chop the rice, my belle no gree me rest. E dey pain me well well and I dey purge. I no fit even chop any other food because of the wahala wey dey my belle."
